{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862572932,"sessionID":"ses_286582029ffeCTIM14Th9MvEPk","part":{"id":"prt_d79a86742001jASZjGLiJp26F5","messageID":"msg_d79a85591001OznlPH62JPCl6V","sessionID":"ses_286582029ffeCTIM14Th9MvEPk","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-e66c0153854645b9b6131e9453a20b9d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-016 Implementation Plan\n2: \n3: **Feature:** AR-016 — PicoD 文件管理 API\n4: **Goal:** 实现完整的文件管理 API，包括文件上传、下载、列表查询、删除、目录创建和元数据查询，提供安全的文件操作能力。\n5: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n6: - DELETE /api/files/*path 支持文件和目录删除，包括递归删除\n7: - PUT /api/files/*path 支持目录创建，包括递归创建\n8: - GET /api/files/*path 支持通过 metadata=true 参数获取详细文件元数据\n9: - GET /api/files 支持通过 recursive 参数递归列出目录内容\n10: - 所有路径操作都经过严格的安全验证（工作空间监狱）\n11: - 实现文件操作锁，防止并发写入冲突\n12: - 所有端点返回统一的 JSON 错误响应格式\n13: - 单元测试覆盖率 >90%\n14: - 集成测试覆盖所有 API 端点\n15: **Architecture:** RESTful API 设计，基于 Gin 框架，JWT 认证保护所有端点，路径安全验证确保工作空间隔离。\n16: **Tech Stack:** Go 1.25, Gin, JWT, 标准库文件操作\n17: **前端验证:** No\n18: \n19: ---\n20: \n21: ### Task 1: Add DELETE handler for file/directory deletion\n22: \n23: **Files:**\n24: - Modify: `pkg/picod/server.go`\n25: - Modify: `pkg/picod/handlers.go`\n26: - Modify: `pkg/picod/errors.go`\n27: - Modify: `pkg/picod/constants.go`\n28: \n29: **Step 1: Write the failing test**\n30: \n31: ```go\n32: // pkg/picod/handlers_test.go\n33: package picod\n34: \n35: import (\n36: \t\"net/http\"\n37: \t\"net/http/httptest\"\n38: \t\"os\"\n39: \t\"path/filepath\"\n40: \t\"strings\"\n41: \t\"testing\"\n42: \n43: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n44: \t. \"github.com/onsi/gomega\"\n45: )\n46: \n47: func TestDeleteFileHandler(t *testing.T) {\n48: \tg := NewGomegaWithT(t)\n49: \n50: \tgin.SetMode(gin.TestMode)\n51: \trouter := gin.New()\n52: \n53: \ttempDir := t.TempDir()\n54: \tserver := &Server{\n55: \t\tworkspaceDir: tempDir,\n56: \t\tauthManager:  nil, // Skip auth for tests\n57: \t}\n58: \n59: \trouter.DELETE(\"/api/files/*path\", server.DeleteFileHandler)\n60: \n61: \t// Create a test file\n62: \ttestFile := filepath.Join(tempDir, \"test.txt\")\n63: \tif err := os.WriteFile(testFile, []byte(\"test content\"), 0644); err != nil {\n64: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"Failed to create test file: %v\", err)\n65: \t}\n66: \n67: \t// Test deleting a file\n68: \treq, _ := http.NewRequest(\"DELETE\", \"/api/files/test.txt\", nil)\n69: \tw := httptest.NewRecorder()\n70: \trouter.ServeHTTP(w, req)\n71: \n72: \tg.Expect(w.Code).To(Equal(http.StatusOK))\n73: \n74: \t// Verify file was deleted\n75: \t_, err := os.Stat(testFile)\n76: \tg.Expect(os.IsNotExist(err)).To(BeTrue())\n77: \n78: \t// Test deleting non-existent file\n79: \treq, _ = http.NewRequest(\"DELETE\", \"/api/files/nonexistent.txt\", nil)\n80: \tw = httptest.NewRecorder()\n81: \trouter.ServeHTTP(w, req)\n82: \n83: \tg.Expect(w.Code).To(Equal(http.StatusNotFound))\n84: }\n85: \n86: func TestDeleteDirectoryHandler(t *testing.T) {\n87: \tg := NewGomegaWithT(t)\n88: \n89: \tgin.SetMode(gin.TestMode)\n90: \trouter := gin.New()\n91: \n92: \ttempDir := t.TempDir()\n93: \tserver := &Server{\n94: \t\tworkspaceDir: tempDir,\n95: \t\tauthManager:  nil,\n96: \t}\n97: \n98: \trouter.DELETE(\"/api/files/*path\", server.DeleteFileHandler)\n99: \n100: \t// Create a test directory with files\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 1784. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-016 Implementation Plan\n\n**Feature:** AR-016 — PicoD 文件管理 API\n**Goal:** 实现完整的文件管理 API，包括文件上传、下载、列表查询、删除、目录创建和元数据查询，提供安全的文件操作能力。\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- DELETE /api/files/*path 支持文件和目录删除，包括递归删除\n- PUT /api/files/*path 支持目录创建，包括递归创建\n- GET /api/files/*path 支持通过 metadata=true 参数获取详细文件元数据\n- GET /api/files 支持通过 recursive 参数递归列出目录内容\n- 所有路径操作都经过严格的安全验证（工作空间监狱）\n- 实现文件操作锁，防止并发写入冲突\n- 所有端点返回统一的 JSON 错误响应格式\n- 单元测试覆盖率 >90%\n- 集成测试覆盖所有 API 端点\n**Architecture:** RESTful API 设计，基于 Gin 框架，JWT 认证保护所有端点，路径安全验证确保工作空间隔离。\n**Tech Stack:** Go 1.25, Gin, JWT, 标准库文件操作\n**前端验证:** No\n\n---\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775862572899,"end":1775862572929}}}}
