{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862604327,"sessionID":"ses_286582029ffeCTIM14Th9MvEPk","part":{"id":"prt_d79a8ddf3001kJY9WZTFI87KRp","messageID":"msg_d79a8b7e2001wHm0IC1B4LfqZ7","sessionID":"ses_286582029ffeCTIM14Th9MvEPk","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-4b71fe3ab9514401bf6c85082e7bafe9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 Implementation Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module**: `pkg/agentd`\n4: **Language**: Go\n5: **Size**: S\n6: **Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n7: \n8: ## Task Breakdown\n9: \n10: ### Task 1: Verify pkg/agentd directory structure\n11: - [ ] Verify pkg/agentd directory exists\n12: - [ ] Create pkg/agentd directory if missing\n13: - [ ] Verify controller.go exists\n14: - [ ] Verify controller_test.go exists\n15: - [ ] Verify constants.go exists\n16: - [ ] Verify metrics.go exists (optional)\n17: \n18: **Verification**: Run `ls -la pkg/agentd/` and verify all required files exist\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ### Task 2: Verify constants.go defines required constants\n23: - [ ] Verify SessionExpirationTimeout constant is defined (15 * time.Minute)\n24: - [ ] Verify LastActivityAnnotationKey constant is defined (\"last-activity-time\")\n25: - [ ] Verify DefaultRequeueInterval constant is defined (30 * time.Second)\n26: - [ ] Verify time package is imported\n27: - [ ] Verify constants have proper documentation comments\n28: - [ ] Verify constant values match design specifications\n29: \n30: **Verification**: Review constants.go implementation and verify all constants are correctly defined\n31: \n32: ---\n33: \n34: ### Task 3: Verify Reconciler struct definition in controller.go\n35: - [ ] Verify Reconciler struct embeds client.Client\n36: - [ ] Verify Reconciler struct has Scheme field (*runtime.Scheme)\n37: - [ ] Verify client package is imported from sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\n38: - [ ] Verify runtime package is imported from k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\n39: - [ ] Verify reconciler package imports are correct\n40: - [ ] Verify struct has proper documentation comments\n41: \n42: **Verification**: Review controller.go and verify Reconciler struct matches design\n43: \n44: ---\n45: \n46: ### Task 4: Implement Reconcile method - Get sandbox resource\n47: - [ ] Verify Reconcile method signature matches controller-runtime Reconciler interface\n48: - [ ] Verify context parameter is accepted\n49: - [ ] Verify req reconcile.Request parameter is accepted\n50: - [ ] Verify agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox is instantiated\n51: - [ ] Verify r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox) is called\n52: - [ ] Verify apierrors.IsNotFound(err) check is implemented\n53: - [ ] Verify reconcile.Result{}, nil is returned for NotFound errors\n54: - [ ] Verify err is returned for other errors\n55: - [ ] Verify proper error wrapping with context\n56: \n57: **Verification**: Test Reconcile method with non-existent sandbox resource\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ### Task 5: Implement Reconcile method - Read and validate annotation\n62: - [ ] Verify sandbox.Annotations is accessed\n63: - [ ] Verify LastActivityAnnotationKey is used to lookup annotation\n64: - [ ] Verify exists check is implemented for annotation\n65: - [ ] Verify empty string check is implemented\n66: - [ ] Verify reconcile.Result{}, nil is returned for missing/empty annotation\n67: - [ ] Verify annotation value is extracted correctly\n68: \n69: **Verification**: Test Reconcile method with sandbox without last-activity-time annotation\n70: \n71: ---\n72: \n73: ### Task 6: Implement Reconcile method - Parse last activity time\n74: - [ ] Verify time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr) is called\n75: - [ ] Verify parsing error is handled\n76: - [ ] Verify error message includes context (\"failed to parse last activity time\")\n77: - [ ] Verify reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: DefaultRequeueInterval} is returned on error\n78: - [ ] Verify error is wrapped with fmt.Errorf and %w\n79: - [ ] Verify lastActivity time variable is stored for later use\n80: \n81: **Verification**: Test Reconcile method with invalid RFC3339 time format\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ### Task 7: Implement Reconcile method - Calculate expiration time\n86: - [ ] Verify SessionExpirationTimeout constant is used\n87: - [ ] Verify expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout) is calculated\n88: - [ ] Verify time.Now().After(expirationTime) check is implemented\n89: - [ ] Verify time.Until(expirationTime) is calculated for RequeueAfter\n90: \n91: **Verification**: Review time calculation logic and verify timeout matches 15 minutes\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ### Task 8: Implement Reconcile method - Delete expired sandbox\n96: - [ ] Verify r.Delete(ctx, sandbox) is called for expired resources\n97: - [ ] Verify apierrors.IsNotFound(err) check is implemented for delete error\n98: - [ ] Verify reconcile.Result{}, nil is returned if resource not found\n99: - [ ] Verify err is returned for other delete errors\n100: - [ ] Verify reconcile.Result{}, nil is returned on successful delete\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 542. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/agentd`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: S\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Verify pkg/agentd directory structure\n- [ ] Verify pkg/agentd directory exists\n- [ ] Create pkg/agentd directory if missing\n- [ ] Verify controller.go exists\n- [ ] Verify controller_test.go exists\n- [ ] Verify constants.go exists\n- [ ] Verify metrics.go exists (optional)\n\n**Verification**: Run `ls -la pkg/agentd/` and verify all required files exist\n\n---","truncated":